				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "First meeting with Karlach, future Origin/Companion. She's a fugitive, wounded and hiding from cultists who are hunting for her to drag her back to hell.\r\n\r\nThe dialogue begins with a stream separating the player and Karlach, as she points a crossbow at them when they approach, holding them at bay. \r\n\r\nShe's fierce, defiant, and intense. But friendly and grateful if the player helps. Shouldn't be too angry - she's in a bad situation and doesn't know who to trust, but she's also been in far worse situations. She has a sense of humour about her predicatment, no matter how bad it gets."
				}
			}
